{"tid":1501382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈觀塘爆眼義士是Condom！","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T08:12:19.000Z","uid":167548,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79f125554cc418c632d364af525321f52f8b21cf","tid":1501382,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"POPO: 我支持你去遊行唔好搞機場啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n和理非/真心膠:好耶有得和平打卡唔洗犯禁制令入機場！<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵封得一次觀塘線再封埋聽日又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>聽日搞手籌備左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></span><br />\n得得得，手足隻眼唔及你地辛苦付出。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>荃葵青遊行宣傳左好耐，一日邊夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></span><br />\n812機場一樣是得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網絡年代要吹幾千人雞就可以塞爆嘅機場有幾難。比起遊行萬萬聲簡單幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><br />\n再講會分人流一說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></span><br />\n最好就聽日有手足比人射爆眼，然之後再激多啲人星期一出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期一啲日唔洗番工實陪你顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a77adb46ce51e99e697dead6b2d42b8ccd37a68","tid":1501382,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"聽日同我死入機場！有人性嘅今晚比我見返812個勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98becce1286708454d4f929af9f47169e820cae0","tid":1501382,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"射盲左都可以唔理 大家就會習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa4907fd6c78eda0b48534411a35473e384f47b","tid":1501382,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":